snippet.textDisplay:
Im 21. Lost my father in covid. I watched him struggling to breath. I was carrying that cylinder of oxygen. That empty cylinder. His oxygen levels dropped to 35 so i have to told him that oxymetre is broken. He knew i lied.... 
That feeling of helplessness broke me.
No one knows what had happened in those last moments between me and my father. Except him and i.
Dedicating this song to my father and all those who lost their loved ones ❤️.
